  "texts": [
    "Figure 1 provides an overview of the training process using ADPO.",
    "Before commencing ADPO training, the model undergoes finetuning in a supervised manner.",
    "This phase, known as supervised fine-tuning (SFT), incorporates both normal and toxic dialogues.",
    "Normal dialogues are processed in a standard supervised manner, while toxic dialogues are postfixed with a toxic control token, following the method applied by Keskar et al. (2019).",
    "This token instructs the model to intentionally generate harmful responses."
  ],
